    let mut demeaned : Vec<f64> = Vec::new();

    for i in (0..mean_vec.len()) {
        demeaned.push(data[i]-mean_vec[i]);
    }

    let demeaned_array = arr1(&demeaned);

    let transformed = pca_component_matrix.dot(&demeaned_array);

    return transformed.to_vec();
}
